          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The thin bismuth layer (3-5-mum) of 10*50-mm area was",
                "evaporated onto a light (7.5-g) aluminum backing.",
                "The backing was then released from the target holder",
                "and used directly for astatine separation via dry",
                "distillation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The At-211 activity was subsequently measured",
                "on a calibrated ionising chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "3CZRUJF"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The U-120M cyclotron."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "INTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The intensity of the beam varied between 10 and",
                " 30-micro-amperes."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The target was irradiated for 1 -2 hours."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. The overall separation yield of At-211 was",
                "found to be 65-75%. The activity of at-211 left in the",
                "target was less than 10%. The most serious losses were",
                "probably due to deposition of astatine on the colder",
                "part of the quartz tube. Separation was finished within",
                "2-hours after EOB."
              ]
            }
          ],
